description: [``botocore``] adds support for AMIs in Recycle Bin
[``botocore``] The release deprecates the use various APIs of RoboMaker Deployment Service in favor of AWS IoT GreenGrass v2.0.
[``botocore``] Add CustomerAWSAccountId to ResolveCustomer API response and increase UsageAllocation limit to 2500.
[``botocore``] Add EC2 Image recycle bin support.
